fields.summary: Impossible to connect a station through WiFi to HGW
[IB5PRO] Gpon is down at boot, also after setting the wan mode and reboot

fields.Action: Connect one 5GHz wifi station and one LAN station to the DUT (Let’s assume that the 5Ghz  station is called PC1 and the LAN station is called PC2)

fields.Expected Result:
Ping is successful and delay is only a couple of ms (Example: A ping of 100ms is not acceptable)

	ICMP echo should be below 50ms

fields.Action:
From PC2 try to ping PC1


	(write down the ICMP results in the measurement field)
fields.Expected Result:
Ping is successful and delay is only a couple of ms (Example: A ping of 100ms is not acceptable)


	ICMP echo should be below 50ms

fields.description: Verify connectivity and latency from 5ghz toward the LAN

security.description: Only SoftAtHome people can access the issue
